					<rich_text>A Pact of Forbidden Arts unlocks spells that are viewed as taboo or outright Evil. Bent on dominating others and inflicting more pain than damage, the Warlock is an aberration of arcane force.</rich_text>
				</node>
				<node custom_icon_id="0" foreground="" is_bold="False" name="Might" prog_lang="custom-colors" readonly="False" tags="" ts_creation="1527344666.44" ts_lastsave="1527371063.82" unique_id="6">
					<rich_text>Wishing to attain strength and fortitude unreachable by regular humans, the Warlock has entered into a pact with a Deity of War, Slaughter or Combat.

Gain increased Strength and Constitution.

Uncanny Stature
The Warlock inspires uneasyness in those who face him. Anyone wishing to attack the Warlock in melee has to pass a Charisma check or suffer Disadvantage on those rolls.

Fearsome Stature
The Warlocks visage is horrid to behold. Any character within 10 meters of the Warlock has to pass a Charisma check or have Disadvantage on all roles directed towards the Warlock for that turn.</rich_text>
				</node>
				<node custom_icon_id="0" foreground="" is_bold="False" name="Knowledge" prog_lang="custom-colors" readonly="False" tags="" ts_creation="1527345038.07" ts_lastsave="1527370651.38" unique_id="12">
					<rich_text>The Warlock has sold his soul in order to attain the knowledge and lore of the ancestral being.

Gain advantage on all knowledge checks.</rich_text>
